# MPJ Tracker

- Multi-user sign-in via Supabase magic link
- Rooms/trades/tasks with per-task photo galleries (saved to Supabase Storage)
- Installable PWA (Add to Home Screen)
- Works on phone/tablet/laptop

## Supabase setup
1. Auth → URL Configuration → Site URL: your Netlify URL (e.g. https://YOUR-SITE.netlify.app)
2. Storage → Create bucket **photos** → make it Public (or readable by `authenticated`).
3. Database:
   - Table: `projects` with columns: `id: text (PK)`, `name: text`, `data: jsonb`
   - RLS: Enable, and add policy to allow `authenticated` users to select/insert/update `projects`.

## Deploy on Netlify
- New site → Import from Git → choose this repo → Build command: (empty), Publish dir: `/` (root).
